# Pages Rules

## Permitted Paths (Write Access)
- `src/pages/**` — all route components

## Approved Reference Paths (Read-Only)
- `src/store/**`
- `src/components/**`
- `src/hooks/**`

## Restricted Paths
- All files under `src/engine/**` (except `src/hooks/useExport.js` integration points)
- All files in `src/components/WidgetRenderer/**` (do not override visual render configurations from pages)

## Container Governance Rules
- Page components serve as logical orchestrators. Keep inline operations minimal and delegate business logic to custom hooks.
- EditorPage coordinates the LeftSidebar, Canvas, and RightPanel states.
- FlowPage uses `@xyflow/react` bindings and Zustand stores. Do not include Konva canvas renderings in the Flow Page.
- ExportPage maps files directly from the codegen coordinator output.
